            <thetext>None of the drag and drop events are buggling events. This is a change to qooxdoo 0.7 where those events did bubble. Further it is inconsistent with the HTML5 drag and drop specification. There are some use cases where it is critical for these events to bubble.

We should make these events bubbling. Note that this change is not API compatible and may break existing code.</thetext>
